                  "content": "Senate Unveils Bipartisan Infrastructure Plan Worth $2.3 Trillion",
                  "lineHeight": 1.15,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 40,
                  "fontWeight": "800",
                  "letterSpacing": -0.5
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
